<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA67">
<l>atuvōnaṉ ṟeṉṟaṅ kamarulakō vēṇṭi</l>
<l>latuvō poruḷillai yaṉṟē yatuvoḻintu</l>
<l>maṇṇiṉṟāḷ vēṉeṉiluṅ kūṭu maṭaneñcē</l>
<l>kaṇṇaṉṟāḷ vāḻttuvatē kal.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As for the pretty desirable world, if you want it, thinking it is good,</l>
<l>it is without value, isn’t it? Leaving it behind,</l>
<l>foolish heart that constantly joins the earth although it says “I am [his] servant”,</l>
<l>learn by praising Kaṇṇaṉ’s feet.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
